---
source: crates/webpkit-cli/tests/snapshot.rs
expression: "dump(\"dwebp\", \"-h\")"
---
$ dwebp -h
dwebp (webpkit) — decode WebP (lossless, lossy, or animated) to PNG/PPM/PAM

Usage: dwebp [options] <input.webp> -o <output>

Options:
  -o <file>      output file (`-` for stdout)
  -png           PNG output (default)
  -ppm / -pam    netpbm output
  -flip          flip vertically
  -alpha         output the alpha plane as grayscale
  -quiet / -v    quieter / more verbose
  -color <when>  auto (default), always, or never
  -version       print version
